quiarritmias auriculares\\N(típicamente fibrilación auricular)","guid":"8gyrPC1reEbYr75WUlddEQ","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"165","text":"↳ Presente en 40-50% de px con DNS (2,8)","guid":"pHDORHK4EezRekQq8XgaCQ","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"165","text":"↳ Asociado a mayor riesgo de eventos CV y mortalidad (2)","guid":"gsuAVlUTGp__vnDc4AyBEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"164","text":"Características\\Nclínicas (2,3)","guid":"M-dtLApuX-TKllODX74IvQ","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"↳ Síntomas varían en intensidad según la extensión de la bradicardia y taquicardia","guid":"E_YjubtK893OVfV91shd8w","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"↳ Síntomas de bradicardia y taquicardia, ej.:","guid":"Twuay1Y3k89d2rVBXWGk0w","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Síncope o presíncope recurrente","guid":"oXo_KLl6PrBdJ7KkTw-_Rg","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"• Palpitaciones","guid":"A_1j1rVLoVMfeM3HFB3uIw","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"171","text":"• Disnea","guid":"bjD-DP1mHTaimArxaa9QLw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"171","text":"• Angina de pecho","guid":"pJnLKglhHloFke6iBWHPwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"169","text":"↳ Síntomas de complicaciones tromboembólicas\\Nasociadas a taquiarritmias auriculares, ej.: ACV","guid":"ZAhK1ngS0xqvMwgoZK0Prg","children":[]}]},{"id":"177","parent":"164","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"1nuPMABzXym7gFXvqyxrzA","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"↳ Estudios diagnósticos\\Nsimilares a DNS","guid":"33uTN6cDuxrbk-5wSnGgTA","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"↳ Anomalías del ritmo: alternancia de taquiarritmias\\Nauriculares (FA, taquicardia auricular, flutter auricular) y\\Nbradicardia (bradicardia sinusal, bradicardia auricular\\Nectópica, pausa sinusal) (3,4,7)","guid":"mAj8TO1s-Qh-tmUrSRvGlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"164","text":"Tratamiento (3)","guid":"pPFPaS3Md9MZ625Qa59x4Q","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"Control de la arritmia","guid":"cJaV3GI5GaOsxaVUfoUFZw","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"↳ Colocación de marcapasos permanente","guid":"0quQEOqKg2xcbIRjMEv-zg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"↳ Tratamiento para taquiarritmias","guid":"zjf5ahhiTuKxR1AOAFJHEA","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"• β-bloqueadores selectivos β1 (cardioselectivos)","guid":"jVlehEGXKZ_YDqSw2oHWYA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"180","text":"• Ver \"Tratamiento de fibrilación auricular\"","guid":"5F2a9hnwikNtHAUZEo_iBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"164","text":"La farmacoterapia para taquiarritmia puede desencadenar bloqueo cardíaco\\Ncompleto, asistolia y bradiarritmias en pacientes sin marcapasos (3).","guid":"1Fmr3n6NYYrbJKZcRrMsWg","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"164","text":"Profilaxis de\\Ntromboembolismo","guid":"3c6o2TWzf3K3s6X446c3dw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"↳ Los px tienen mayor riesgo de eventos CV","guid":"viGfsnV6cazTO_kLMo3pnA","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"↳ Evaluar necesidad de anticoagulación según factores de riesgo del px y tipo de taquiarritmia\\N(ver \"Anticoagulación en fibrilación auricular\")","guid":"CWKbaH0oJw7_DpNFBN7geQ","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":189,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/General","filename":"Enfermedad del nodo-2024","id":"map_737","resolved_references":[]}